<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Converse2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Converse,</orth> vb., 1) to associate, to hold intercourse: <bibl n="shak. tgv 1.3.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. I, 3, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.4.63" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 4, 63</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.861" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 861</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 1.2.78" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. I, 2, 78</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 3.4.12" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 4, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.2.66" default="NO" valid="yes">As V, 2, 66</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.494" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 494</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.1.75" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B V, 1, 75</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.1.25" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 1, 25</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.1.195" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B II, 1, 195</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.368" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 368</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.2.28" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 2, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.1.56" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 1, 56</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 1.4.16" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 4, 16</bibl>.<lb />2) to talk, to discourse: <bibl n="shak. err 2.2.162" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. II, 2, 162</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 4.1.183" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado IV, 1, 183</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.1.6" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 1, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.4.81" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 4, 81</bibl>.
